#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Cartesian exponent of species of types]

Given species of types $F: Uu_(1) ->  Uu_(2)$ and $G Uu_(1) ->  Uu_3$, we define the cartesian exponent of $F$ and $G$ at $X : Uu$ as the pointwise exponent
$
  "cart-exp"(F,G)(X) := F(X) -> G(X)
$
